snippet.title: TOP SIX UNISEX AMBER FRAGRANCES: If You LOVE AMBER Then You MUST SMELL THESE
snippet.description:
Six best amber fragrance from my perfume collection. Today I am talking everything amber, and sharing with you the top six amber perfumes that you need to add to your fragrance collection ASAP. Amber has quickly become one of my favourite fragrance notes, after my love for vanilla. Amber is such a warm and inviting perfume note that works so well on men and women. I really enjoy smelling seductive and sexy, and wearing these makes me feel that way. So today, I thought I would rank the six amber fragrances I have in my perfume collection. I will be sharing with you exactly how these fragrances smell and will give you my rating. These six fragrances are some of the best perfumes for men and women in the winter, but some of these fragrances can be worn in the summer too. I will mention the king of amber grand soir, but also discuss some newer releases like Carolina Herrera Amber Desire. Stay tuned to see what my favourite amber fragrances are.
